title: Chris Cornell and David Arnold - Casino Royale Soundtrack
description:
From 2006 Casino Royale movie (DVD).

Track list:
Chris Cornell - You know my name
David Arnold - James Bond theme

Format: 6-channel FLAC (level 8)
Source: DVD (DTS audio track)

Note: All tracks are taken right from the movie, with some in-movie audio at the beginning. While i think i can cut it off if necessary, i see no reason to do that. This isn't the first case when soundtrack music contains movie sounds.

Note2: "You know my name" song is NOT included in official Casino Royale movie soundtrack and is distributed separately. Also, this version of "You know my name" (from the movie) is different from the MP3 version ( http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3566747/Chris_Cornell_-_You_Know_My_Name.mp3 ), for more details read Wikipedia - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/You_Know_My_Name .
